</h2>

<div class="video-grid">

<div class="video-card">

<iframe
src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fUR55xr-Zv4"
allowfullscreen>
</iframe>

<h3>
General Prosperity Prayer
</h3>

<p>
Secrets of Maharaj Monu Baba.
</p>

</div>

<div class="video-card">

<iframe
src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/l8Uh7IeYknk"
allowfullscreen>
</iframe>

<h3>
Removing Negative Energy
</h3>

<p>
Removing Negative Energy with Angels.
</p>

</div>

<div class="video-card">

<iframe
src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/eenpqYDLKS4"
allowfullscreen>
</iframe>

<h3>
Address of Belur Lokenath Mandir
</h3>

<p>
Find the Temple Location.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="section">

<div class="container">

<h2>
Latest Videos
</h2>

<div class="video-grid">

{
latestVideos.map(video => (

<div class="video-card">

<a
href={`https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=${video.id}`}
target="_blank"
rel="noopener noreferrer">

<img
src={video.thumbnail}
alt={video.title}
/>

</a>

<h3>
{video.title}
</h3>

